description:
Bobo has a nightmare audition.

Khalyla gives Pacman a pass... sort of.

Gilbo is triggered to tears.

We talk radioactive watermelons, a butterfinger stash, and why Maurice hates Asians.

 

Recorded February 22, 2016

Music by Bobby Lee
